How Put Works Internally
Steps:
Compute hash of key
Find bucket index
Check:
If empty → insert
If key exists → update value
If collision → add to list/tree
If size exceeds threshold → resize

Capacity, Load Factor, Rehashing
Capacity = Initial size = 16
Load Factor = Default = 0.75
Threshold =  capacity × loadFactor
👉 When size crosses threshold → rehash (resize)

Rehashing
Capacity doubles
All elements redistributed
👉 Costly operation → O(n)


